WEBVTT

00:00:07.000 --> 00:00:09.301
Huh?
This is a weird turn.

00:00:09.461 --> 00:00:12.821
Hello. I'm Nishimura from Baiking, the
dream contractor.

00:00:12.821 --> 00:00:13.821
Huh?

00:00:13.821 --> 00:00:19.181
So today, we're heading to Takara-kun, who
lives deep in the mountains...

00:00:19.901 --> 00:00:22.641
to deliver him a piping-hot pizza.

00:00:22.641 --> 00:00:23.521
What a sudden genre shift.
Hang tight.

00:00:23.521 --> 00:00:25.762
Huh?
Huh? Different show?

00:00:25.862 --> 00:00:30.322
No way that's a real escape-room tactic.
Hahaha.

00:00:30.502 --> 00:00:32.762
People would roast you online for that.
They'd roast you online.

00:00:33.382 --> 00:00:35.822
A pickaxe? People would be like, what is
this? Amazing.

00:00:36.182 --> 00:00:40.322
Since they said anything goes, it's like
they really lent him a pickaxe.

00:00:41.463 --> 00:00:44.843
If you did that in an escape room, the
second player couldn't do anything. You'd owe damages.

00:00:45.123 --> 00:00:48.343
The second player would just walk through.
Hahaha.

00:00:48.543 --> 00:00:53.943
But that's fine. That's how it is. Use
whatever works. Yeah, exactly.

00:00:54.303 --> 00:00:56.103
Yeah.
As long as you get out.

00:00:56.103 --> 00:00:59.784
Oh, it opened.
That's incredible. Seriously.

00:01:02.264 --> 00:01:04.944
We dug a lot.
Wanna try?

00:01:05.164 --> 00:01:06.404
Let's try it.
Think you can fit?

00:01:06.704 --> 00:01:08.304
Wait.
Takano should go first.

00:01:09.224 --> 00:01:11.504
Please, let this work.
Go, go, you're going.

00:01:11.504 --> 00:01:17.125
If this doesn't work, I'm screwed.
Hahaha.

00:01:17.125 --> 00:01:18.125
Ah.

00:01:21.145 --> 00:01:23.945
This is a real escape.
Amazing if we get out from here.

00:01:25.765 --> 00:01:30.065
Don't break it. Don't force it.
Can you pull just this bit off?

00:01:30.065 --> 00:01:30.986
Here.
Yeah.

00:01:30.986 --> 00:01:33.266
Yeah, yeah.
Okay.

00:01:33.746 --> 00:01:34.746
Whoa.
Oh, it went through.

00:01:35.386 --> 00:01:37.686
Hahaha.
That's insane.

00:01:37.686 --> 00:01:38.646
What?
I can get out.

00:01:38.646 --> 00:01:41.126
I can get out?
Really?

00:01:41.806 --> 00:01:43.286
Huh?
Takano?

00:01:43.626 --> 00:01:46.086
I can get out, I can get out.
You can?

00:01:46.086 --> 00:01:47.567
I can get out, I can, I can.
Good, go!

00:01:47.567 --> 00:01:48.947
I'm going, I'm going.
Seriously?

00:01:48.947 --> 00:01:50.087
I'm going.
Okay.

00:01:50.167 --> 00:01:51.167
Go!
Whoa!

00:01:51.647 --> 00:01:53.067
Ah!
Amazing!

00:01:53.327 --> 00:01:54.367
Outside! Outside!
What?!

00:01:55.467 --> 00:01:58.587
That can happen?
Huh? It's morning.

00:01:59.067 --> 00:02:00.587
It's morning?
He did it, he did it!

00:02:01.007 --> 00:02:04.468
You can do it, you can do it.
Takano, go!

00:02:04.468 --> 00:02:05.928
Go! No way!
We're really outside.

00:02:06.588 --> 00:02:08.348
Seriously?
What kind of place is this?

00:02:08.888 --> 00:02:11.108
He's out! He's out!
Whoa, he's out!

00:02:11.568 --> 00:02:13.188
He's out! It's a jailbreak.
He's out!

00:02:15.348 --> 00:02:17.968
He's out!
Hahahahaha.

00:02:18.748 --> 00:02:21.369
You made it out!
Thank God.

00:02:22.089 --> 00:02:23.729
So this is what a jailbreak feels like.
Congratulations.

00:02:24.129 --> 00:02:26.549
We escaped.
I'm going too.

00:02:26.989 --> 00:02:28.509
You can do it?
Seriously?

00:02:28.509 --> 00:02:29.649
Yeah.
Amazing.

00:02:29.689 --> 00:02:31.909
Amazing.
This place is gross.

00:02:32.589 --> 00:02:35.549
You can do it?
Whoa, I'm actually getting nervous.

00:02:36.870 --> 00:02:41.010
It feels so open out here.
Go, go, go.

00:02:41.570 --> 00:02:43.110
Whoa.
Whoa.

00:02:43.110 --> 00:02:45.050
I can get out, I can get out.
You really dug that out.

00:02:45.130 --> 00:02:47.130
Seriously.
At this size.

00:02:47.430 --> 00:02:49.830
It's not roomy at all,
but all I can see is the way out.

00:02:49.930 --> 00:02:51.090
Look at all that dirt.
Hahaha.

00:02:51.150 --> 00:02:54.451
Everything's catching. You never see this
much dirt on variety TV.

00:02:54.691 --> 00:02:56.811
You can do it, you can do it.
You can make it?

00:02:57.951 --> 00:03:01.111
Whoa.
Whoa.

00:03:01.111 --> 00:03:02.291
Ah! Go, go, go.
Go, go, go. It's morning!

00:03:02.291 --> 00:03:05.431
Hahaha.
It's like a movie.

00:03:05.611 --> 00:03:06.911
We're out!
Yes!

00:03:06.971 --> 00:03:10.812
Amazing!
Yes!

00:03:10.812 --> 00:03:14.492
Unreal. How many dirt-crawl scenes are we
gonna get?

00:03:14.932 --> 00:03:17.232
Amazing.
Like Kuro-chan too.

00:03:17.392 --> 00:03:18.732
What is this place?
It's morning.

00:03:18.732 --> 00:03:21.892
Six in the morning.
Wow, this is nuts.

00:03:21.972 --> 00:03:25.212
Where are we?
It's nothing like inside.

00:03:25.472 --> 00:03:28.813
Looks nothing like the interior.
So that's what that white room was.

00:03:28.933 --> 00:03:30.713
That was satisfying.
It's just a shack.

00:03:31.233 --> 00:03:33.873
Hahaha.
Seriously, where are we?

00:03:35.333 --> 00:03:37.873
