Which way do we go? What's out there?

00:03:48.015 --> 00:03:50.335
This isn't a 'good job, everyone' moment.
What prefecture are we in?

00:03:50.955 --> 00:03:51.955
Oh.
This.

00:03:52.235 --> 00:03:56.175
This is bad.
It's morning, but seriously, where are we?

00:03:57.395 --> 00:04:00.816
Creepy.
There really is nothing here.

00:04:01.616 --> 00:04:04.116
Watch it.
It's cold, for starters.

00:04:04.176 --> 00:04:07.036
Let's just go home.
It obviously looks freezing.

00:04:07.036 --> 00:04:08.076
That hurts.
Ow.

00:04:08.276 --> 00:04:11.576
Can we go now? I mean, we finally...
finally got out.

00:04:12.957 --> 00:04:14.817
No.
Whoa.

00:04:15.077 --> 00:04:18.677
There's nothing here.
This is deep in the sticks.

00:04:18.677 --> 00:04:19.237
It's cold.
It's cold.

00:04:19.237 --> 00:04:21.137
