There's nobody here.

00:04:21.197 --> 00:04:23.197
So what now?
Seriously, how do we get home?

00:04:23.337 --> 00:04:24.938
What?
There's more ahead?

00:04:24.938 --> 00:04:27.358
Wow, this is wild.
