We may have to beg someone for a ride.

00:04:48.160 --> 00:04:50.840
Oh, oh, oh.
Maybe someone's coming.

00:04:51.100 --> 00:04:55.900
Ah.
Huh?

00:04:57.040 --> 00:04:59.200
Oh, it doesn't hurt at all now.
Oh, good, good.

00:04:59.200 --> 00:05:00.601
