Hey.

00:05:00.601 --> 00:05:02.601
Oh, really?
A person.

00:05:02.981 --> 00:05:04.281
Oh.
Okano?

00:05:04.281 --> 00:05:05.081
Hey.
No way!

00:05:05.081 --> 00:05:06.601
Huh?
Whoa, incredible.

00:05:07.171 --> 00:05:08.171
Mr. Okano.
Hey!

00:05:08.171 --> 00:05:08.861
It's Okano.
Hey!

00:05:08.861 --> 00:05:10.141
It's Okano.
It's Okano.

00:05:10.621 --> 00:05:12.442
Nice! Wow, this is amazing.
Whoa. Whoa.

00:05:12.442 --> 00:05:18.722
Nice.
