You got completely trashed, right?

00:05:40.024 --> 00:05:42.124
Same for you?
We were in a white room.

00:05:43.044 --> 00:05:44.344
What?
No, ours was pitch black.

00:05:44.344 --> 00:05:46.384
A pitch-black room.
Pitch black.

00:05:46.484 --> 00:05:50.785
