What do we do now?

00:05:54.085 --> 00:05:57.565
We came from over there.
Look, I was trapped back there.

00:05:57.565 --> 00:05:58.565
Huh?
Uh...

00:05:58.785 --> 00:06:00.926
Oh, that weird place.
Seriously...

00:06:00.946 --> 00:06:02.806
That was terrifying.
For real.

00:06:03.366 --> 00:06:08.526
But there's nothing here either. It's some
village, but nobody's around. Like a deserted settlement.

00:06:08.526 --> 00:06:09.926
There's nothing?
Nothing at all.

00:06:09.926 --> 00:06:11.606
Nothing.
Nobody's here.

00:06:11.927 --> 00:06:13.327
Probably.
Shoes, shoes.

00:06:13.327 --> 00:06:16.147
Weird way to say shoes.
This is rough.

00:06:16.207 --> 00:06:18.927
No way, these muddy ones?
So gross.

00:06:19.087 --> 00:06:21.627
Seriously.
Can I just take one?

00:06:22.227 --> 00:06:25.068
Lend me one.
I'm barefoot.

00:06:25.308 --> 00:06:27.068
