Yeah, probably.

00:06:46.429 --> 00:06:48.610
This is definitely Wednesday.
I knew it.

00:06:49.130 --> 00:06:52.710
Whoever came up with this is insane.
Yeah, seriously.

00:06:53.890 --> 00:06:56.650
