Exactly. Where's the 'just a bit' in this?

00:06:57.690 --> 00:06:59.550
Right? Probably that much...
Even this...

00:07:00.271 --> 00:07:02.071
Can you even laugh at this?
Can this even air?

00:07:02.251 --> 00:07:04.051
No way this airs.
That room over there... huh?

00:07:05.411 --> 00:07:06.451
Oh.
Whoa.

00:07:06.451 --> 00:07:07.451
Whoa.
Whoa.

00:07:07.691 --> 00:07:09.871
What?
Whoa, amazing.

00:07:10.211 --> 00:07:14.152
You okay?
You okay?

