00:07:29.653 --> 00:07:35.173
I had to eat all the candy and break a
hole in the wall to get out. Brutal.

00:07:35.173 --> 00:07:36.154
Brutal.
Seriously.

00:07:36.154 --> 00:07:40.994
Insane. I ate so much sugar my brain
nearly shorted out.

00:07:41.014 --> 00:07:42.234
Ugh, that's disgusting.
Anyway...

00:07:42.234 --> 00:07:43.714
Google?
No, seriously.

00:07:44.274 --> 00:07:45.534
Let's just get out of this village
already. This is bad.

00:07:45.814 --> 00:07:47.874
How do we get out?
I even smoked on an empty stomach.

00:07:47.914 --> 00:07:50.515
Exactly. Enough chatter, let's just move.
How do we get out of here?

00:07:50.855 --> 00:07:51.995
What is this?
What even is it for?

00:07:52.135 --> 00:07:54.475
So he's joining us too?
That's scary.

00:07:54.935 --> 00:07:59.135
They still don't know. They still don't
know there's one more person.

00:07:59.215 --> 00:08:01.896
Ugh.
No.

00:08:01.976 --> 00:08:03.836
Ugh.
This is bad.

00:08:03.836 --> 00:08:05.456
Worst-case scenario.
Ugh.

00:08:05.456 --> 00:08:06.396
Scary.
Scary.

00:08:06.396 --> 00:08:08.936
Then that's definitely it.
That's definitely it.

00:08:08.936 --> 00:08:11.936
It's definitely that.
Why is everyone here?

