00:08:25.577 --> 00:08:26.757
What?
What?

00:08:27.278 --> 00:08:28.378
True enough.
Come over here.

00:08:28.818 --> 00:08:30.838
Poor guy.
This is on a whole different level.

00:08:30.898 --> 00:08:32.558
Poor guy.
This is the worst.

00:08:32.738 --> 00:08:34.238
Come over here.
Come here.

