Used it, and...

00:09:11.001 --> 00:09:12.001
Oh.
And then...

00:09:12.181 --> 00:09:16.941
Then, you know, a dog dug for us and saved
us. I don't understand a single thing.

00:09:17.532 --> 00:09:18.532
A dog?
There's a dog here?

00:09:19.562 --> 00:09:21.662
The dog digs for you.
Calm down, calm down.

00:09:21.942 --> 00:09:24.282
Explain it properly.
This makes no sense.

00:09:24.302 --> 00:09:25.602
So if Kuro-chan's here,
right, right.

00:09:25.962 --> 00:09:28.382
I see, it's starting to connect.
What's "right" supposed to mean?

00:09:28.402 --> 00:09:31.283
The only show crazy enough to do this
