and they were like, no, it's a streaming show.

00:09:47.844 --> 00:09:51.924
So they actually called it a streaming
show? My memory's fuzzy, though.

00:09:52.164 --> 00:09:53.904
Makes sense.
It was a while ago.

00:09:53.984 --> 00:09:58.205
