00:10:06.465 --> 00:10:08.785
Here, take this.
Seriously.

00:10:08.845 --> 00:10:11.506
Wow.
That helps a lot.

00:10:11.806 --> 00:10:14.106
Ow.
That's nice.

00:10:14.106 --> 00:10:14.906
So nice.
Ow.

00:10:14.906 --> 00:10:19.506
Even though you're barely hanging on
yourself. Still makes a big difference.

00:10:20.446 --> 00:10:22.466
Yeah.
Can I at least get your gratitude?

00:10:22.466 --> 00:10:23.466
Just your gratitude.
Come on.

00:10:26.067 --> 00:10:29.087
Thanks.
Kind of annoying, though.

00:10:29.167 --> 00:10:30.567
What the hell?
No, no...

00:10:30.727 --> 00:10:32.887
It's fine.
Now's not the time. Poor guy's suffering.

00:10:33.087 --> 00:10:34.987
Let's go.
Let's go.

00:10:35.067 --> 00:10:37.488
Let's go.
Kuro-chan, if you die...

00:10:37.628 --> 00:10:38.788
Ow, ow, ow.
Ow.

00:10:38.848 --> 00:10:41.628
This place is scary.
Scary.

00:10:42.788 --> 00:10:46.588
