Still hilarious, though.

00:10:48.809 --> 00:10:52.989
If you find anything, give it to me.
Seriously. Just watching you walk is funny enough.

00:10:53.429 --> 00:10:55.089
It hurts.
Has for a while.

00:10:55.209 --> 00:10:58.289
There are loads, look.
Be grateful.

00:10:58.649 --> 00:10:59.649
Be grateful.
Whoa.

00:10:59.889 --> 00:11:03.410
Whoa.
Shoes, footwear, anything to wear.

00:11:03.890 --> 00:11:05.650
Thank you.
Thank you.

00:11:05.710 --> 00:11:06.990
Futon.
See? This is it.

00:11:06.990 --> 00:11:07.910
Look, look, look.
Look.

00:11:07.910 --> 00:11:11.410
Yeah, even so...
There's enough for everybody.

00:11:11.430 --> 00:11:13.330
There is, there is.
There's some here too.

00:11:13.350 --> 00:11:15.891
Teacher, this is your moment, teacher.
Slippers.

00:11:15.911 --> 00:11:19.011
Wow, I'm so happy.
They're warm.

00:11:19.091 --> 00:11:23.151
Good for you.
Good for you.

00:11:23.151 --> 00:11:23.711
